!                                                                             !
! 8080 ASSEMBER OPERATION LABELS                                              !
!                                                                             !
! Defines the operator labels used in the 8080 assembler, both machine codes  !
! and pseudo operators.                                                       !
! Use the following command to convert this file:                             !
!                                                                             !
!    hashtab op8080                                                           !
!                                                                             !
! The resulting file, op8080.res, will contain an opcode type definition,     !
! to be merged into md8080.pas, and a resym table initalizer, to be placed    !
! in ut8080.pas.                                                              !
! You also need to take the last value of opcode, and place this in the       !
! hash call at fndres in ut8080.pas.                                          !
!                                                                             !
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

